headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Car Meet Prize Ride and Challenge
content:
Outmaneuvering the cops on your own is one thing but flooring it with sirens in your rearview and a chopper overhead while trying to find the fastest route from A to B is a completely different flavor of chaos.

LS Car Meet members who manage to place Top 4 in 8 different Pursuit Series Races will earn the keys to the Dinka RT3000, to tweak and freak as they see fit.
